EmailTemplate.name: PBP Additional Documents
EmailTemplate.subject: Post Billpay Setup – Additional Documents
EmailTemplate.textOnly:
Dear {!Apttus__APTS_Agreement__c.Apttus__Primary_Contact__c},
Thank you for the opportunity to provide you with our Post Billpay solution. To allow us to proceed, we require you to complete the attached documents;
1. Australia Post Credit Application (confirming your agreement to the terms of credit for use with Australia Post) 2. Australia Post Biller Application (to allow the setup and provision of agency services) 3. Questionnaire (to allow the plan and design of your Post Billpay solution)
If you have any questions regarding the completion of these documents, do not hesitate to call me. Best Regards, {!Apttus__APTS_Agreement__c.OwnerFirstName} {!Apttus__APTS_Agreement__c.OwnerLastName}
Australia Post is committed to providing our customers with excellent service. If we can assist you in any way please telephone 13 13 18 or visit our website.
